      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "汉钟离、吕洞宾、张果老、蓝采和、曹国舅、李铁拐、韩湘子、何仙姑同进。",
      "text_length": 34
